{"data":[{"id":560521337,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560521337","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545847348,"updated_time":1545965446,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":14,"content":"\u003cp\u003e首先想正面回答一下提问者的问题。如果你真的证明出了哥德巴赫猜想，也就无非两种情况:一是你通过自学了解了数学届的很多定理，深刻掌握数论，并能熟练运用，再通过自己严谨的思维推演完成证明；另一种则是利用初高中或是大学本科阶段一些浅显的知识，在机缘巧合下想到了证明方法并完成证明。就前一种情况来说，无疑你可以得到全国乃至全世界任何一所大学的offer，也可以轻易取得任何你感兴趣的成就。但就后一种而言，就算你真的证明出来了，清北也不一定要你，因为就人才的选取方面，你紧紧只是一个高中生，几乎什么都不懂的高中生，唯一和其他高中生不同的是，你的思维比较灵敏，对待问题勇于探索，但这又有什么用呢，我相信被挡在清北门外的人中并不缺这种角色。不错，你可能确实解决了世界难题，但是你连解决数学（其他）问题的一点理论基础都没有或者说不牢固，清北凭什么收你？！可能清北招生办随便拿出一张全国奥林匹克竞赛试题就能让你做不下去，清北又怎么敢要你？！这就好比一个好吃懒做的乞丐突然中彩票一百万，但对于只会好吃懒做的人而言，再多的钱也只是白纸，再怎么富有也只是昙花一现，无法引的世人瞩目。综上，若你是第一种人，你不必担心这个问题（可能也不会想这个问题）；若你是第二种人，你不用担心这个问题，就算你证明了哥猜，清北也未必录你，而哥猜证明对你的意义就是会在你的人生简历中留下浓墨重彩的一笔，但也就仅此而已。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e说这么多，并不是说要打击你，相反我特别欣赏你，因为你在小小年纪已经表现出同龄人少有的探索精神与求知欲望，唯一不足的就是，你对这个世界还了解甚少，也就是说心智还不够成熟，总想着一步登天这种不切实际的事。所以，我想说的是，请你继续保持对知识的渴求的欲望与勇往直前的探索精神，无论成功与否，请务必坚持，当你慢慢长大成熟，认清现实本身，同时却也保持着对知识的纯真，我相信，你终会成功的！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实题主做的事我相信我们大多数人小的时候都做过:就是，听说，什么什么从来没有人做到过，这时你们肯定回想如果我做到了会怎么样？会受到奖励吗？会荣誉加身吗？等等。而唯一不同的是，题主很有可能确实努力去做了这所谓的没人完成的事，也有可能确实做到了，然后就是将心中的疑问放在社交媒体上以寻求答案。仅此而已。所以，还是希望大家不要太多的冷嘲热讽，致使一位少年失去了对知识原本的渴求与探索精神！！尽管他可能还太年轻，但也请给他留点时间和空间让他成长起来，去认识世界美好的一面！！ \u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560913692,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"4b85011e25a8d4a13e26d13cb0043947","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560913692","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545898601,"updated_time":1545898601,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e如果证明了哥德巴赫猜想，可以考虑一下更好的学校。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563771093,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"f7a3d095f968de256881256dbc076ea0","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563771093","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546274992,"updated_time":1546315827,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e业余数学爱好者究竟能不能证明这一猜想呢?\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e    徐迟在《哥德巴赫猜想)一文中描写陈景润第一次听到哥德巴赫猜想的情景时写道:“当老师介绍了这一猜想后,学生们吵吵嚷嚷地认为没什么了不起。第二天就有几个相当用功的学生给老师送来答案,宣称哥德巴赫猜想已经证明。 \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e   老师说:‘你们算了吧,白费这个劲干什么?你们这些卷子我是看也不会看的,用不着看的。那么容易吗?\u003cb\u003e你们是想骑着自行车到月球上去\u003c/b\u003e。”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e   数学所陆柱家处长解释说,如果一个人没有良好的高等数学基础,不了解一些非常现代的数学方法就想证明哥德巴赫猜想,就好比拿着改锥、锯、刨子造一架航天飞机,你说你造出来了,谁信呢?假如能用初等数学的方法证明,那么也早就被人证明了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.fx361.com/page/1998/0820/3900417.shtml\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e哥德巴赫猜想:你能骑自行车上月球吗?_参考网\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e而根据 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e 给出的“\u003cb\u003e证明\u003c/b\u003e”，这孩子能不能上三本都是问题。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563769256,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"f85936480f256c33a7cf24a787c9aa57","url_token":"zhi-yu-shui-59","name":"鲸不是鱼","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-58e9684825f129d8c255f52c8f47514c_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-58e9684825f129d8c255f52c8f47514c_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/f85936480f256c33a7cf24a787c9aa57","user_type":"people","headline":"“借给我”“要做什么用啊？”“买女人”","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563769256","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-fe6e26713cc270f1d1d11d099a5bd7aa_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546274786,"updated_time":1546274789,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e这个弟弟的证明还真是拍出来的照片。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e记得之前有人怀疑他会不会编辑数学符号。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e只用了三页半\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我的建议是，去复读吧\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-fe6e26713cc270f1d1d11d099a5bd7aa_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"360\" data-rawheight=\"474\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d560e6bf00c6dfc9ba9b65bc2f24b50c_b.jpg\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"360\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='360'%20height='474'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"360\" data-rawheight=\"474\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d560e6bf00c6dfc9ba9b65bc2f24b50c_b.jpg\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"360\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-fe6e26713cc270f1d1d11d099a5bd7aa_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561407486,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"ee103ca77607f3cae75e5306bfa6a094","url_token":"luo-xie-21-11","name":"落叶","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/1d5ccf6905329fb9814dc0bec2ab9286_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/1d5ccf6905329fb9814dc0bec2ab9286_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/ee103ca77607f3cae75e5306bfa6a094","user_type":"people","headline":"不正常人类心理学研究精神病征患者","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561407486","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545965399,"updated_time":1545965399,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e对于高考，你的智商已经让你意识到了困难\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e面对哥猜，你的学识不足以让你看到其困难\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e就酱\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560437371,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a056cc4b9cc34fbb9c87356ead9e65fe","url_token":"Simengtun","name":"司萌豚","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f7763641c4d1d42297778671c7e768b4_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f7763641c4d1d42297778671c7e768b4_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a056cc4b9cc34fbb9c87356ead9e65fe","user_type":"people","headline":"无能的人","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560437371","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545837658,"updated_time":1545934190,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e泻药。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e保送什么的我不懂，但是你如果真证出来了，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那孙一峰就是我二哥。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e——补充一点——\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我看高赞里张益唐的意思是说You said calculation.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e——再补充一点——\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我看陈景润的意思是年轻人好好〇〇，不要〇〇〇〇了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a057b3339cb9af07449b7e6dd234feca_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"187\" data-rawheight=\"173\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"187\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='187'%20height='173'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"187\" data-rawheight=\"173\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"187\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a057b3339cb9af07449b7e6dd234feca_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e——接着补充——\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我觉得你可以参考下高赞里杨振宁对廖某的回复。比张益唐还要简练。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e什么？你找不到？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可这就是杨振宁的回复啊\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561424669,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561424669","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545966625,"updated_time":1545967555,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我发现这个问题底下\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e回答里面觉得答题的人都恶意满满的主页点进去都是没有科研经历或者对理工科完全没概念的人，觉得应该对题主鼓励啊，应该鼓励创新，他还只是个孩子啊，又不会造成影响。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我想如果你如果天天搞科学研究到两点，为了一道数值问题会花几个小时，甚至只是为了装一个matlab就等了很久的人，当你看到这个问题和题主有关的回应时，内心应该和我一样愤怒。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我是一个数学本科的学生，曾经的我，也觉得自己特别聪明，对理工科也没有什么概念，我相信那个时候的我如果看到这个问题也会这么想，凭什么不给我们机会，凭什么说我们是错的；但是当我学习了数学的有关课程，数学分析，高等代数，偏微分方程，数值计算，实变函数这些科目的时候，那些头秃的日日夜夜，那些抓狂的瞬间。我现在非常能理解题目下那些说侮辱科学的人的心情，当你视之如珍宝的东西被别人这样践踏，你的心情只会比现在更愤怒。你没有了解科研工作者理工科的辛苦你又凭什么指责我们恶意满满呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e相反和我们一样理工科的知乎大v，他们就能理解我们的苦，但他们可能比我们考虑的周到，既提出了问题，也不乏劝告，可以说是很温暖的人了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePS:题主我高中跟你心境差不多，但是也没想过解决哥猜这种问题，只觉得自己高考肯定能上清华北大，我也不像其他答主推荐你看什么数论了，毕竟数学本科到目前为止也没接触到，我建议你看一下华东师范的《数学分析》（都不用看苏联的卓里奇和菲赫金哥尔茨）这是数学系最最最基础的课程了，然后做一下吉米多维奇的习题，当然你觉得没必要拘泥于什么课本上的内容我也没办法，但是大厦不是一下建成的，基础必须得有。就算研究量子力学的科学家，他们对经典力学理解也是非常深的\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560224624,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"d2d156cbd8c2c303240412611de46cae","url_token":"obersteinlee","name":"obersteinlee","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-bc438bd7f11c09dffe5bead96e8d9e23_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-bc438bd7f11c09dffe5bead96e8d9e23_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/d2d156cbd8c2c303240412611de46cae","user_type":"people","headline":"人虎","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560224624","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545820026,"updated_time":1545820026,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我辈以心证道，可以去起点发表\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560809298,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"edb63ca6d0e2d62dc6b3085c8c216aa8","url_token":"liu-ze-pei-19","name":"Jeanskon Lowsan","avatar_