真的证出来了吗\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e欢迎打脸，毕竟连知乎官方都会连带着打脸，我这算啥啊 ️\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-10496c4f23615e27ba892790e2ee4aca_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-93983ba3ee88eafe5f106b99a5261628_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-10496c4f23615e27ba892790e2ee4aca_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='1920'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-93983ba3ee88eafe5f106b99a5261628_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-10496c4f23615e27ba892790e2ee4aca_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-10496c4f23615e27ba892790e2ee4aca_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561312415,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"fbc1e04027f27ce885c975875c4e6269","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561312415","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545957799,"updated_time":1545957799,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e等到造反以后当了皇上 我就可以封自己当地主了\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559907372,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"609309e89dac3fd1a627f62da88c4297","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559907372","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545792893,"updated_time":1545792893,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":11,"content":"\u003cp\u003e这么说的人别说不懂数学了，连基本的科研都不懂。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个世界早就不是你一个人闭门造车的时代了。如果你有接近证明哥猜的能力，那你早就出名了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e很多数学概念和想法，并不是自己学能学好的，再怎么天赋异禀的人也需要和人交流讨论，而一旦和人交流讨论就自然会让人知道几斤几两。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以，如果你有那个能力，就算没证明也早就该出名了，该进大学也早就进了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e另外，如果你真的拿出了证明，等别人看出你对错，弄不好已经过了好几年了……\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559679083,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"6cb363eb2d8224480d10a76000e56187","url_token":"star-46-59","name":"star","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/6cb363eb2d8224480d10a76000e56187","user_type":"people","headline":"物理/科幻","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559679083","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-89c636438925366af107833d0aeed596_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545750770,"updated_time":1545750770,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":9,"content":"\u003cp\u003e你可以在清北自招的面试中提及你的自我炒作能力，可能有点用\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e毕竟一个能较为精准地抓住受众的痛点和网络媒体的爆点的高中生还是不错的，比如，，，，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一，利用受众对于哥猜和清北的关注度\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e二，利用哥猜，清北和普通高中生之间的强对比度\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e三，预定时间，制造痛点\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0b960d5ff1f99db45527fbc4a6c58361_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1125\" data-rawheight=\"2436\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e38cf6ac0e4a2d5116f58d58ec469b9c_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1125\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0b960d5ff1f99db45527fbc4a6c58361_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1125'%20height='2436'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1125\" data-rawheight=\"2436\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e38cf6ac0e4a2d5116f58d58ec469b9c_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1125\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0b960d5ff1f99db45527fbc4a6c58361_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0b960d5ff1f99db45527fbc4a6c58361_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e不得不说效果还蛮不错的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-8fa47d90c9929895b3c105d38a93fc81_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1123\" data-rawheight=\"1244\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-2