\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然，至于你能不能通过清北自招初审就，，，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e毕竟还是一个目标在河北大学的，连空间向量都搞不定的高中生嘛 \u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7da1ddbae39919c7fb2065be83ef5100_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1125\" data-rawheight=\"2436\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-124b48f3dcd8fc70dcfd740f9f80d665_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1125\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7da1ddbae39919c7fb2065be83ef5100_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1125'%20height='2436'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1125\" data-rawheight=\"2436\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-124b48f3dcd8fc70dcfd740f9f80d665_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1125\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7da1ddbae39919c7fb2065be83ef5100_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7da1ddbae39919c7fb2065be83ef5100_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c6d82d89e2a8fa51949a5123f8d4bf31_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1125\" data-rawheight=\"2436\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-fe5b8f071545acd45290dd31eca04cad_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1125\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c6d82d89e2a8fa51949a5123f8d4bf31_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1125'%20height='2436'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1125\" data-rawheight=\"2436\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-fe5b8f071545acd45290dd31eca04cad_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1125\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c6d82d89e2a8fa51949a5123f8d4bf31_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c6d82d89e2a8fa51949a5123f8d4bf31_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560718800,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"624836b266374237cebfe483aea4c170","url_token":"tulip2130","name":"WHite","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-08a0456a9305ce831879567686efe250_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-08a0456a9305ce831879567686efe250_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/624836b266374237cebfe483aea4c170","user_type":"people","headline":"为了未来，奋斗现在","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560718800","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545881716,"updated_time":1545881716,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":9,"content":"\u003cp\u003e为什么很多人一定要这样去嘲讽，这只是一名高中生的热情，难道不应该指出他的错误，让他有更成熟明确的研究方向吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我想那些冷言冷语的人一定是忘了自己高中时过着怎样的生活，至少在我的印象里，那是一段对什么事都充满好奇，渴望去发掘真相的岁月，不怕笑话，高中我一度沉迷量子理论，到处吹牛逼，但是到了大学，一方面是因为专业选了工科，另一方面是在大物中接触了实际的量子理论各种蛋疼公式后产生了退缩，于是老老实实继续做了个工科男，但是我心里对量子理论的热爱也从未熄灭，关注了科学院的一些公众号，有什么新发现都乐于去了解一下。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对于题主我是有一些共鸣的，但我相信他的热情更甚于我，对此我的看法是，不要让你的梦因为知乎上的各路大佬泼冷水而熄灭，你能真正证明出哥猜甚至更多谜题的可能性一定是有的，现在只是个开始，不代表你是错的，只是你并没有真正的完成这份证明，还有许多细节需要进一步发掘，至于能否成功，就看你能否在短暂的人生中去捕捉到那微弱的希望。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e另外，上述所说的一切要建立在你读了一个还算过得去的大学，中国教育体制确实有其问题（否则法国学生也不至于集体游行反对建立全国统一招生录取平台），但是你现在需要做的是在这个体制下为自己争取到能更好实现你愿望的平台，暂时将这个哥德巴赫猜想证明的雏形放在一边，在这个人生最重要的考试中给出漂亮的结果是第一要事，否则真的进个二本三本，我想周围几乎没人愿意钻研的氛围里你也坚持不下去。嗯，能竞赛拿奖保送是最好的，这一点就算到了大学也不变，都在争着拿奖保研。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后，如果你对于数学的热情和我一样，其实仅仅是浮于表面的简单了解，那这些终归会消退，想清楚后尽早站出来澄清，大家不会真的纠结于高中生尚且幼稚的梦，就像我，你其实仅仅是没有给这个梦的种子灌输足够的养分罢了，但你还有无数别的种子，人生会很精彩的。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559412147,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"8d58d1181437b55e07578490cd402381","url_token":"er-bao-zhu","name":"毛毛","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-9cab26dec397eace096b5ad3bc1d8c31_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-9cab26dec397eace096b5ad3bc1d8c31_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/8d58d1181437b55e07578490cd402381","user_type":"people","headline":"学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559412147","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545724766,"updated_time":1545724766,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":9,"content":"\u003cp\u003e可以看看华罗庚的经历：初中毕业以后，一边工作一边自学高中和大学低年级的全部数学课程。在杂志上发表了几篇数学论文，被清华大学数学系主任熊庆来看重，直接调到清华当图书管理员，第二年开始担任清华数学助理、然后是助教、讲师。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个初中文凭的天才，没有在清华读书，直接去清华当老师。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561984608,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"9814fcef08486c982cd79d637936b825","url_token":"jing-chen-chen-29","name":"越努力越幸运","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-950e270b623c3d190562777ef156ee7f_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-950e270b623c3d190562777ef156ee7f_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/9814fcef08486c982cd79d637936b825","user_type":"people","headline":"命，是弱者的借口；运，是强者的谦词。","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561984608","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546040743,"updated_time":1546040743,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":9,"content":"\u003cp\u003e题主如果真的具有十几岁证明哥猜的能力，这样的数学天赋应该早就被发现了吧，少年天才嘛，也许几年前参加某某竞赛就可以一举成名，早就可以准备走竞赛保送的路子了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e个人认为，题主应该是数学知识体系以及对哥猜的认知尚浅，在自己的认知范围内认为证明没有问题，但是搞数学的应该一眼就能看出来问题所在。希望等公布证明以后，证明错了，你能虚心接受批评，放平心态，脚踏实地准备高考。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然，如果，，如果被题主证明哥猜这种小概率事件发生了，那么也恭喜题主，希望保持初心，继续有所作为。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e等你公布结果，看看各位数学相关知乎er给的建议吧。还是奉劝一句，不要在不具有相匹配的实力的时候妄图走捷径，脚踏实地吧。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560469744,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"7f5e8d9357c6b62eb14821bb81267708","url_token":"mei-yuan-tao","name":"用户名","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/7f5e8d9357c6b62eb14821bb81267708","user_type":"people","headline":"学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560469744","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545840281,"updated_time":1545840281,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":11,"content":"\u003cp\u003e问这样的问题，佩服你也欣赏你，不论你证明正确与否，我要承认你现在真的是在学数学，我高中学的，那叫考试。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559800029,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"3ce3b6a6d09fa2cae7fbce5ed1bc59b9","url_token":"xiao-ze-ma-da-ha","name":"小泽马大哈","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/3cc371f8b_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/3cc371f8b_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/3ce3b6a6d09fa2cae7fbce5ed1bc59b9","user_type":"people","headline":"梦想是在北大办个设计学院，ENFP","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559800029","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545783125,"updated_time":1545783125,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e高中生真证出来的，那就是百年一遇不世出的天才，别说保送本科了，直接给教授职位估计都有可能。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e假装证出来的，如果有一篇洋洋洒洒但是有漏洞的东西，包装包装还是可以用的，起码表明了对数学的兴趣和和一定基础，估计能够在自主招生过程中起到些作用，但直接保送可能比较难。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=320\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=280\u0026sort_by=default","totals":2283}}
